FAQs
What are $MHONEY NFT
$MHONEY is an NFT and community project started by a group of friends passionate about art, cryptocurrency and meeting new people. Our team has a great technical and artistic vision that prefers to underpromise and overdeliver. We'll share more information as our community grows and will give all our efforts in everything we do.
When will nft's launch?
We're working very hard on the collection to release soon. We'll share more information as soon as we can and hope to make it as soon as possible.
I want to collaborate with $MHONEY. What should I do?
For business and partnership inquiries, please contact our twitter account https://twitter.com/.
What can you expect from being part of $MHONEY?
You can expect to be part of an interactive community that will reap the rewards from the success of our project that we build together. The most important thing for us is to reward members who are active in contributing to the quality and expansion of our community. Our team values genuine interactions with fellow reapers that will stimulate the project’s growth and create a healthy community. Just be yourself and enjoy what we create together!
